          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-links">
          <a href="mailto:justincadburywong@gmail.com">justincadburywong@gmail.com</a>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/justin-cadbury-wong">LinkedIn</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/justincadburywong">GitHub</a>
          <a href="/JustinWongResume202605.pdf" download>Resume</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
